@endpoint POST /draft_registrations/{draft_id}/relationships/subjects/
@desc Add subjects to a draft registration
@required {draft_id: any # The unique identifier of the draft registration., body: map # JSON:API list of subject identifiers to associate with the draft registration.}
@returns(204) Subjects added successfully.
@errors {403: Forbidden. You don't have permission to modify subjects., 404: Draft registration not found.}

@endpoint DELETE /draft_registrations/{draft_id}/relationships/subjects/
@desc Remove subjects from a draft registration
@required {draft_id: any # The unique identifier of the draft registration., body: map # JSON:API list of subject identifiers to disassociate from the draft registration.}
@returns(204) Subjects removed successfully.
@errors {403: Forbidden. You don't have permission to modify subjects., 404: Draft registration not found.}

