@returns(200) Subscription successfully updated.
@errors {400: Bad Request. The request body is malformed or missing required fields., 401: Unauthorized. Authentication credentials are missing or invalid., 403: Forbidden. You do not have permission to modify this subscription., 404: Not Found. The subscription or provider does not exist.}

